connector-forge
Copyright 2026 Giuseppe (connector-forge author)

This product includes a generalist agent skill for building verified
connectors (MCP / CLI / API / file / browser / desktop) for any application
surface.

The skill was distilled from field work on three real benches:
  - ValuAziende OneMaster Bridge (FastAPI/React, native governance)
  - Archicad 29 (desktop CAD via add-on)
  - Oracle Primavera P6 (enterprise scheduling, standalone SQLite)

The benches appear in this repository only as sanitized case studies.
No proprietary method, no scoring formulas or thresholds, no user data,
no credentials, and no private portfolio data are included.

Authored collaboratively by Giuseppe (operator / domain author) with the
assistance of AI agents (Claude, OpenAI Codex, and others) acting under the
operator's command and verification.
